[normal]The British Association for Counselling and Psychotherapy (BACP) would like to submit the following response to the Health Committee’s Inquiry into 
[normal]the Management of 
[normal]L
[normal]ong-term 
[normal]C
[normal]onditions
[normal] (LTCs)
